item.title: Cyber Security Events
item.description: TechXLR8 2017 Location: Excel, London Event type: Technology Expo/Festival Event Photos: TechXLR8 is a festival of technology taking you on a journey, between networks, Tech and consumer services, connecting industries and opening up new markets. TechXLR8 will showcase 8 leading technology events, giving you the opportunity to get the insights and build the relationships you need to be part of the fully Connected Future. With a shared exhibition and a comprehensive multi-track conference, TechXLR8 will enable you to better understand the infrastructure supporting the tech of tomorrow and the services and industries that will benefit from this fast evolving world.
